title: Bracket - Complete Discography
description:
The absolutely complete discography of Bracket.  The Giant Midget EP isn't listed because the only track that isn't on 924 Forestville St. is "Imaginary Friend."

-4 Rare Vibes
-4-Wheel Vibe
-5:35
-924 Forestville St.
-"E" is for Everything on Fat Wreck Chords
-Like You Know
-Live in a Dive
-Novelty Forever
-Requiem
-When All Else Fails

As well as these songs from compilations, etc.:
-867-5309, Jenny
-Hearing Aid
-Imaginary Friend
-Warren's Song Part 8


I hope some other people will enjoy Bracket as much as I do.
